🎙HUMP DAY PODDY...OUT NOW!🎙
.
Happy Wednesday everyone. This week’s GUEST is a brave young lady called Michelle. We talk about her sexual assault, her battle with cancer, terminating a pregnancy, and much more. 🙌

As always, thanks for tuning in! 💙
@mmmshells our absolute pleasure!! It was lovely to meet you. Thank YOU for sharing your inspiring story with us. 💙🙏

You guys are so incredible! Thank u so much for your time ♥️🙌🥰
Truely an inspiration team xx
@simone_tara_gsd enjoy!! @mmmshells is an amazing young lady. 🙌
Looking forward to some quiet time tomorrow with a cuppa and listening to a great podcast☕️👌🏼☺️💙
@narah_roscio aww! We feel so privileged that she opened up and shared her story with us. So lucky to have met her! What an incredible lady. 💙🙌
@narah_roscio ♥️♥️♥️ you are so beautiful!! I absolutely adore you 🙏 thank you for support xx
@mmmshells is such an inspirational beautiful strong woman that always lights up the room when you are with her😍
@angela_l_c7 that is lovely. It sounds like Michelle has such a supportive family. She has such a powerful story. 💙
@angela_l_c7 love u so much! I’m so lucky to have you as my aunt ♥️
Truly amazing and so very proud of my beautiful niece @mmmshells - always here for you ❤️❤️
@3dmag very well said!! She is amazing. Everyone needs to hear her inspiring story of overcoming adversity. 💙
Michelle you are an incredibly, strong, inspirational woman and I respect and admire your strength... you definitely are a survivor 😘😘
@lymphomaaustralia very brave young lady! Wonderful role model. 💙
Thank you for sharing your story and experience with non-hodgkin lymphoma @mmmshells
